%section#banner.section-featured
  #carousel-example-generic.carousel.slide{"data-ride" => "carousel"}
    / Indicators
    %ol.carousel-indicators
      %li.active{"data-slide-to" => "0", "data-target" => "#carousel-example-generic"}
      %li{"data-slide-to" => "1", "data-target" => "#carousel-example-generic"}
      %li{"data-slide-to" => "2", "data-target" => "#carousel-example-generic"}
    / Wrapper for slides
    .carousel-inner
      .item.active
        .row.header-text
          .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
            .text-center
              %i.fa.fa.fa-thumbs-up.fa-5x
              %h2.slogan FoodBanker Makes Giving Easy!
              %p
                The USDA reports that almost 40% of our entire food supply goes to waste every year. Don't waste your surplus food, donate it, and do it easily, and hassle free with FoodBanker on the web or on your phone.
      .item
        .row.header-text
          .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
            .text-center
              %i.fa.fa.fa-thumbs-up.fa-5x
              %h2.slogan FoodBanker Connects Communities!
              %p
                FoodBanker isn't only for those looking to donate. It's for those looking to recieve and distribute. Get notifications when local donors have surplus, schedule your operations better by following donors who give regularly.
      .item
        .row.header-text
          .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
            .text-center
              %i.fa.fa.fa-thumbs-up.fa-5x
              %h2.slogan Connect In More Ways Than One
              %p
                FoodBanker helps Donors and Distributers get surplus food from those who have to those who need. It connects them through localization system and FoodBanker Gameify's the experience to encourage more donations, and socializes it to promote community interaction.
    / Controls
    %a.left.carousel-control{"data-slide" => "prev", :href => "#carousel-example-generic"}
      %span.fa.fa-chevron-left
    %a.right.carousel-control{"data-slide" => "next", :href => "#carousel-example-generic"}
      %span.fa.fa-chevron-right
  / /carousel
%section.section.section-services
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-4
        %i.fa.fa-code.fa-5x
        %h4
          %strong EASY DONATING
        %p
          Quick sign up and set up connects donors and recipeints in minutes. Donors quickly notify recipients with a single touch.
      .col-lg-4
        %i.fa.fa-terminal.fa-5x
        %h4
          %strong LOCALIZATION
        %p
          Users save time and money by being connected to the nearest donors or recipients through the localization system.
      .col-lg-4
        %i.fa.fa-bolt.fa-5x
        %h4
          %strong TIMELINESS
        %p
          Give anytime or on a schedule with a quick give button, or regularly through easy setup of recurring donation intervals.
